\hypertarget{ux5b8cux6210ux4ee5ux4e0bux64cdux4f5c}{%
\subsubsection{\texorpdfstring{\textbf{完成以下操作}}{完成以下操作}}\label{ux5b8cux6210ux4ee5ux4e0bux64cdux4f5c}}

\begin{itemize}
\tightlist
\item
  定义一些变量（比如 x, y , z 并赋值；内容随意）
\item
  从外部文件装入一些数据（可自行创建一个4行5列的数据，内容随意）
\item
  保存workspace 到.RData
\item
  列出当前工作空间内的所有变量
\item
  删除当前工作空间内所有变量
\item
  从.RData文件恢复保存的数据
\item
  再次列出当前工作空间内的所有变量，以确认变量已恢复
\item
  随机删除两个变量
\item
  再次列出当前工作空间内的所有变量

\hypertarget{ux7ec3ux4e60ux4e0eux4f5cux4e1a2factorux57faux7840}{%
\subsection{练习与作业2：Factor基础}\label{ux7ec3ux4e60ux4e0eux4f5cux4e1a2factorux57faux7840}}

\begin{center}\rule{0.5\linewidth}{0.5pt}\end{center}

\hypertarget{factorux589eux52a0}{%
\subsubsection{\texorpdfstring{\textbf{factor增加}}{factor增加}}\label{factorux589eux52a0}}

\begin{itemize}
\tightlist
\item
  创建一个变量：
\end{itemize}

\texttt{x\ \textless{}-\ c("single",\ "married",\ "married",\ "single");}

\begin{itemize}
\item
  为x增加 两个 levels，\texttt{single}, \texttt{married};
\item
  以下操作能成功吗？
\end{itemize}

\texttt{x{[}3{]}\ \textless{}-\ "widowed"};

\begin{itemize}
\tightlist
\item
  如果不，请提供解决方案；
\end{itemize}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\DocumentationTok{\#\# 代码写这里，并运行；}
\NormalTok{x }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"single"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"married"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"married"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"single"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{x }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{factor}\NormalTok{(x, }\AttributeTok{levels =} \FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"single"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"married"}\NormalTok{))}
\FunctionTok{try}\NormalTok{(x[}\DecValTok{3}\NormalTok{] }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \StringTok{"widowed"}\NormalTok{)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{verbatim}
## Warning in `[<-.factor`(`*tmp*`, 3, value = "widowed"): 因子层次有错，产生了NA
\end{verbatim}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\# 解决方案}
\NormalTok{x }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{factor}\NormalTok{(x, }\AttributeTok{levels =} \FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"single"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"married"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"widowed"}\NormalTok{))}
\FunctionTok{try}\NormalTok{(x[}\DecValTok{3}\NormalTok{] }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \StringTok{"widowed"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{x}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{verbatim}
## [1] single  married widowed single 
## Levels: single married widowed
\end{verbatim}

\begin{center}\rule{0.5\linewidth}{0.5pt}\end{center}

\hypertarget{ux5229ux7528factorux6392ux5e8f}{%
\subsubsection{\texorpdfstring{\textbf{利用factor排序}}{利用factor排序}}\label{ux5229ux7528factorux6392ux5e8f}}

以下变量包含了几个月份，请使用\texttt{factor}，使其能按月份，而不是英文字符串排序：

\texttt{mon\ \textless{}-\ c("Mar","Nov","Mar","Aug","Sep","Jun","Nov","Nov","Oct","Jun","May","Sep","Dec","Jul","Nov");}

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\DocumentationTok{\#\# 代码写这里，并运行；}
\NormalTok{mon }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"Mar"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Nov"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Mar"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Aug"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Sep"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Jun"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Nov"}\NormalTok{,}
  \StringTok{"Nov"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Oct"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Jun"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"May"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Sep"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Dec"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Jul"}\NormalTok{,}\StringTok{"Nov"}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{mon }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{factor}\NormalTok{(mon, }\AttributeTok{levels =} \FunctionTok{c}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"Jan"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Feb"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Mar"}\NormalTok{,}
  \StringTok{"Apr"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"May"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Jun"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Jul"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Aug"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Sep"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Oct"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Nov"}\NormalTok{, }\StringTok{"Dec"}\NormalTok{))}
\FunctionTok{sort}\NormalTok{(mon)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\begin{verbatim}
##  [1] Mar Mar May Jun Jun Jul Aug Sep Sep Oct Nov Nov Nov Nov Dec
## Levels: Jan Feb Mar Apr May Jun Jul Aug Sep Oct Nov Dec
\end{verbatim}

\begin{center}\rule{0.5\linewidth}{0.5pt}\end{center}

\subsubsection{\texorpdfstring{\textbf{画图}}{画图}}\label{ux753bux56fe}}

\begin{enumerate}
\def\labelenumi{\arabic{enumi}.}
\tightlist
\item
  用 readr 包中的函数读取 mouse genes 文件 （从本课程的 Github 页面下载
  data/talk04/ ）
\item
  选取常染色体的基因
\item
  画以下两个基因长度 boxplot :
\end{enumerate}

\begin{itemize}
\tightlist
\item
  按染色体序号排列，比如 1, 2, 3 \ldots. X, Y
\item
  按基因长度 中值 排列，从 短 -\textgreater{} 长 \ldots{}
\end{itemize}
